<package xmlns="http://www.idpf.org/2007/opf" unique-identifier="epubmerge-id" version="2.0">
  <metadata xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:opf="http://www.idpf.org/2007/opf">
    <dc:title>The Book of HPMOR Fanfics</dc:title>
    <dc:creator opf:role="aut" opf:file-as="Various Muggles">Various Muggles</dc:creator>
    <dc:identifier id="epubmerge-id">epubmerge-uid-1593090960</dc:identifier>
    <dc:contributor opf:role="bkp">calibre (4.19.0) [https://calibre-ebook.com]</dc:contributor>
    <dc:rights>Copyrights as per source stories</dc:rights>
    <dc:description>&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p id="comments"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;T&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;his anthology contains:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;01. Seventh Horcrux by Emerald Ashes&lt;br&gt;02. Squibgineering by credentiality&lt;br&gt;03. Tom Riddle – Origins of a Dark Lord by user1444&lt;br&gt;04. Tom Riddle and the Conflict of Interest by user1444&lt;br&gt;05. Tom Riddle and Battle Magic 2 by user1444&lt;br&gt;06. Tom Riddle and Conflicts of Christmas by user1444&lt;br&gt;07. Firenze's Tale by Lanthanum&lt;br&gt;08. Lord Voldemort's First Speech by Achille-Talon&lt;br&gt;09. Professors Aren't Idiots by Meneldur&lt;br&gt;10. Hermione Granger and the Perfectly Reasonable Explanation by Robin.Drew&lt;br&gt;11. Mary Poppins Begins the End by ElizabethRobinThales&lt;br&gt;12. Daystar's Remix of HPMOR by DaystarEld&lt;br&gt;13. HPMOR Crack: A Questionable Harry Potter by Appliciousness&lt;br&gt;14. Chapter 10a Hufflepuff Harry Potter by Anonymous&lt;br&gt;15. Headmaster Potter-Evans-Verres by GreatestKingOfThemAll999&lt;br&gt;16. Minerva McGonagal and the Sensible Course of Action by Phigment&lt;br&gt;17. HPMoR: The Missing (but Necessary) Chapters by qbsmd&lt;br&gt;18. Hysteresis by JustMcShane&lt;br&gt;19. One Level Deeper by superdupervenience&lt;br&gt;20. Harry Potter and the Technique of Quidditch by jgf1123&lt;br&gt;21. Memories are Golden and Death is Cheap by Lewis The King&lt;br&gt;22. Nightmares of Azkaban by Owl344&lt;br&gt;23. The Fallacy of Division By Zero by kyrilu&lt;br&gt;24. Harry's Game by Black Logician&lt;br&gt;25. Educational by centreoftheselights&lt;br&gt;26. Dark Lord Material by TheallknowingandUnseen&lt;br&gt;27. Following the Phoenix by hezzel&lt;br&gt;28. Following the Phoenix - Flashes by hezzel&lt;br&gt;29. Squiring the Phoenix by EagleJarl&lt;br&gt;30. Once Upon A Tower by TheOtherSarshi&lt;br&gt;31. Hermione Granger and the Burden of Responsibility by Squirrelloid&lt;br&gt;32. Depart Azkaban by ThinkingSpeck&lt;br&gt;33. A Strip of Cloth by laurelinwen&lt;br&gt;34. Proximity by 75th&lt;br&gt;35. Innocence by linkhyrule5&lt;br&gt;36. For Summer by Be3&lt;br&gt;37. Asking for Help by qbsmd&lt;br&gt;&lt;s&gt;38. Hermione Granger and the Tesseract of Merlin by Writingathing&lt;/s&gt;&lt;br&gt;39. HPMoRCh 89 AU by Ialdabaoth&lt;br&gt;40. Reductionism for the Win by qbsmd&lt;br&gt;41. Repairing Ignorance by rumblestiltsken&lt;br&gt;42. Harry Potter and the Philosopher's Zombie by alexanderwales&lt;br&gt;43. The Longest Day by NanashiSaito&lt;br&gt;44. Griphook and the Strong Form EMH by SooperGeenius&lt;br&gt;45. Hacking the Source of Magic by qbsmd&lt;br&gt;46. Harry Potter and the cryptographic key by greatcactus&lt;br&gt;&lt;s&gt;47. Of Fakes Phoenixes and Friendship by Anonymous&lt;/s&gt;&lt;br&gt;48. Minds Names and Faces by ShutUpAndCalculate&lt;br&gt;49. Nothing Left but Fire by aphyer&lt;br&gt;50. Alt Chapters 109-110 (Riddles Upon Riddles, Legacy of The Troll) by Anonymous&lt;br&gt;51. Still In(,) The Mirror by Lilgreenman&lt;br&gt;52. The Last Enemy by asthiathien&lt;br&gt;53. HPMoR the final exam by Psychoticpotatodwarf&lt;br&gt;54. Exam Answer by WestWard101&lt;br&gt;55. Near Mode Far Mode by abiggerhammer&lt;br&gt;56. Harry Potter and the Nuclear Bomb by greatcactus&lt;br&gt;57. A Rational Response by NeutralWotan&lt;br&gt;58. Final Revision by H Bregalad&lt;br&gt;&lt;s&gt;59. Methods of Fictionality by Anonymous&lt;/s&gt;&lt;br&gt;60. Nonlinear Regression by Anonymous&lt;br&gt;61. Chapter 113 Exam Answers by Various&lt;br&gt;62. How HPMoR Should Have Ended by Markus Ramikin&lt;br&gt;63. The Philosopher's Red Herring by White Squirrel&lt;br&gt;64. Revival by xingxingzf&lt;br&gt;65. Harry Potter and the Irrational Odyssey by ElizabethRobinThales&lt;br&gt;66. Stephen and the Plans of Harry James Potter-Evans-Verres by space fountain&lt;br&gt;67. Harry Potter and the Methods of Self-Modification by bsen&lt;br&gt;68. You Said No Kissing by wordbug&lt;br&gt;69. Don't Think of a Strangelet by SooperGeenius&lt;br&gt;70. The Universe is an Optimisation Problem by notasentientantcolony&lt;br&gt;71. Hermione Granger and the Other Side-Effect by foxtales&lt;br&gt;72. Ginny Weasley and the Methods of Rationality by XNecateX&lt;br&gt;73. Harry Potter and the European Empire by Eleventh Century Remnant&lt;br&gt;74. On the Continuity of Consciousness by al_fa&lt;br&gt;75. Hermione Granger and the Price of the Phoenix by linusmir&lt;br&gt;76. Harry Potter and the Memories of a Sociopath by qbsmd&lt;br&gt;77. Draco Malfoy and the Practice of Rationality by taogaming&lt;br&gt;78. Ginny Weasley and the Sealed Intelligence by BayesWatch&lt;br&gt;79. Ginny Weasley and the Sealed Intelligence, Chapter 7: HiSHE by The M M&lt;br&gt;80. Sirius Black and the Prisoner's Dilemma by Avret&lt;br&gt;81. Dennis and the Academy by dances-alone&lt;br&gt;82. Harry Potter and the Order of Chaos by centreoftheselights&lt;br&gt;83. Orders of Magnitude by 2PIH&lt;br&gt;84. Significant Digits by adeebus&lt;br&gt;85. To Boldly Go by Khyron42&lt;br&gt;86. A Crack/Slash Epilogue by alexanderwales&lt;br&gt;87. Harry Potter and the Methods of Chaos by JBean210&lt;br&gt;88. How Wizards Do Money by nicoledieker&lt;br&gt;89. Oh God Not Again! by Sarah1281&lt;br&gt;&lt;s&gt;90. Not a victim MrVoldemort by Kensu&lt;/s&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;s&gt;91. Harry Potter and Selective Perception by Anonymous&lt;/s&gt;&lt;br&gt;92. Moore &amp;amp; Boole by Jethro Harrup&lt;br&gt;93. Harry Potter and the Natural 20 by Sir Poley&lt;br&gt;94. Harry Potter and the Confirmed Critical by Sir Poley&lt;br&gt;95. Harry Potter and the Save-or-Die by Sir Poley&lt;br&gt;96. A Black Comedy by nonjon&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</dc:description>
    <dc:date>0101-01-01T00:00:00+00:00</dc:date>
